description: 'Kids Day in Riverdale': To celebrate the 100th issue of this digest featuring Archie and his friends, the editors at Archie Comics have taken a trip down memory lane, courtesy of the classic Archie animated TV series. This all-new story has been fashioned using screen grabs from the legendary Saturday morning cartoon show!
